## Instructions
1. Extract chronological events mentioned in the article.
2. For each event provide: date (as precise as available), event_description, event_type (founding/discovery/publication/battle/election/award/death/other), and participants (people/organizations involved).
3. Sort events chronologically. Return [] if no datable events are found.

## Output Format
